query: SELECT br.*, ig.name as toIslandName FROM boat_routes br LEFT JOIN island_guides ig ON br.toIslandGuideId = ig.id WHERE br.toIslandGuideId = 10 OR br.toLocation LIKE '%Ukulhas%';
